name: Cuttle Fishin' 2: The New World
description:
Developed by pumibless (Michelle) and ysong (You Jin) 

You precious  cuttlefish is hungry for the food! press space bar to move around the beautiful ocean and collect all the clams clear the level.

This is a sequel game from the game of Cuttle-fishin' developed by Nicole Polidore (Nicole Polidore) and Xen98 (Daniel Han). Here is a link to try out: https://xen98.itch.io/cuttle-fishin. In this game players explore the ocean and collect objectives to complete and go to the next level, using the space bar.  Compare to the first game, we have changed several mechanics and background so play to check it out!
